  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766310/extras/6c61720400ee56674faa570d3fab800e.poster.avif?t=1733594423\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766310/extras/6c61720400ee56674faa570d3fab800e.webm?t=1733594423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766310/extras/6c61720400ee56674faa570d3fab800e.mp4?t=1733594423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766310/extras/ea671f1ed4252ab53b7975ce4914c42b.poster.avif?t=1733594423\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766310/extras/ea671f1ed4252ab53b7975ce4914c42b.webm?t=1733594423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766310/extras/ea671f1ed4252ab53b7975ce4914c42b.mp4?t=1733594423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>From the maker of Zombie Death Quota.<br>Use Gyro Aim to Paint and Power Slide your way around while defeating Monsters, building platforms and avoiding the deadly Squog (Square Fog).<br>Multiple game modes to test your skill in paint coverage, speed and aim.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>6 different Paint Splodgers.<br></li><li>Lots of Power Ups and items.<br></li><li>Single Player and up to 4 Local Players for Co-op and Versus.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Splodge Royale: Paint more of the world than your friends, as the fog closes in.<br></li><li>Battle Royale: Hide or fight as the fog closes in.<br></li><li>KingZone: Find and paint the Zones. <br></li><li>Charged: Battle between points to transfer energy.<br></li><li>Passport: Collect enough gold and evacuate before your friends do, place traps to slow them down.<br></li><li>Overpaint: Repaint enough of the old paint.<br></li><li>Skate: Collect enough gold before the time runs out.<br></li><li>Storm Race: Avoid the fast moving fog.<br></li><li>Survival Race: Avoid the fog and defeat monsters.<br></li><li>Collect and Conquer: Defeat monsters and collect gold.</li></ul>",
