es. <br></li><li>Charged: Battle between points to transfer energy.<br></li><li>Passport: Collect enough gold and evacuate before your friends do, place traps to slow them down.<br></li><li>Overpaint: Repaint enough of the old paint.<br></li><li>Skate: Collect enough gold before the time runs out.<br></li><li>Storm Race: Avoid the fast moving fog.<br></li><li>Survival Race: Avoid the fog and defeat monsters.<br></li><li>Collect and Conquer: Defeat monsters and collect gold.</li></ul>",
